title: Matt Furie - Boy's Club
description:
Haaahahaahaha! I laughed, regularly and often. Of course, that could be because these characters reminded me of people I actually know. lol

-----------------------------------------------------------

Boy's Club 1-2

Teenage Dinosaur, 2006, 44 pages
Buenaventura Press, 2008, 44 pages

Written and Illustrated by Matt Furie

Recommended for anyone who had fun being a teenage to to mid-twenties male living a more, uhh, alternative lifestyle (and by that I mean... drugs! lol). Or for anyone who knew somebody like that, as well
